t wide black borders on all sides.  Is this not an NTSC console?</div><br />I thought SDTV NTSC was 4:3<br /><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/480i" class="postlink">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/480i</a>

		

